Hmm.

I've been thinking about MSC. I unlocked ERQ, selected her, and went to the warehouse level. And it was early early morning, just daybreak, and ERQ was there alone. I went up to Winona's cabin and she was asleep on the couch.

My interpretation of this is that ERQ makes time early in the morning to practice when no one is around. She is, like Morgan, driven to excel, and pursues that end in a solitary manner, without distractions. The ancient Greeks said that realization of one's true potential was a moral virtue, which they called arete. I have to approve of the way she puts in the work.
